{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1", "title": "Aidan Steele's blog (usually about AWS)", "home_page_url": "https://awsteele.com/", "feed_url": "https://awsteele.com/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "Here's my seventh or eighth attempt at a blog.  It's mostly going to be my experimentation with using AWS (Amazon Web Services, not Aidan William Steele).", "icon": null, "authors": [{"name": "Aidan W. Steele"}], "language": "en", "items": [{"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2023/02/20/a-role-for-all-your-ec2-instances.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2023/02/20/a-role-for-all-your-ec2-instances.html", "title": "A role for all your EC2 instances", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2023-02-20T22:12:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2023/12/19/an-aws-iam-identity-center-vulnerability.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2023/12/19/an-aws-iam-identity-center-vulnerability.html", "title": "An AWS IAM Identity Center vulnerability", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2023-12-19T20:40:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS", "OIDC"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2021/09/06/api-gateway-http-apis-and-sqs-messageattributes.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2021/09/06/api-gateway-http-apis-and-sqs-messageattributes.html", "title": "API Gateway HTTP APIs and SQS MessageAttributes", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2021-09-06T07:37:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2026/07/01/apps-can-now-impersonate-human-access-to-aws-via-iam-identity-center.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2026/07/01/apps-can-now-impersonate-human-access-to-aws-via-iam-identity-center.html", "title": "Apps can now impersonate human access to AWS via IAM Identity Center", "content_html": "<p>Earlier today, AWS IAM Identity Center [launched][launch] the ability for server-side\napplications to assume roles on behalf of their users. This is a big deal, I've\nwanted this exact kind of functionality for years. The docs are pretty sparse\non how it works and what the events look like in CloudTrail, so here are my\nfield notes, recommendations on whether you should use it today and feature\nrequests for whichever AWS service team is working on this.</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2026-07-01T02:40:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS", "OIDC"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2020/09/26/aws-access-key-format.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2020/09/26/aws-access-key-format.html", "title": "AWS Access Key ID formats", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2020-09-26T00:40:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2021/09/15/aws-federation-comes-to-github-actions.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2021/09/15/aws-federation-comes-to-github-actions.html", "title": "AWS federation comes to GitHub Actions", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2021-09-15T02:37:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS", "GitHub", "OIDC"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/01/20/aws-gwlb-deep-packet-manipulation.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/01/20/aws-gwlb-deep-packet-manipulation.html", "title": "AWS GWLB: Deep Packet Manipulation", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2022-01-20T00:53:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2020/09/29/aws-iam-needs-resourceorgid.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2020/09/29/aws-iam-needs-resourceorgid.html", "title": "AWS IAM needs aws:ResourceOrgID", "content_html": "", "image": nul