2-02-03T04:48:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/12/16/centralised-logging-from-cloudwatch-to-kinesis-firehose.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/12/16/centralised-logging-from-cloudwatch-to-kinesis-firehose.html", "title": "Centralised logging: from CloudWatch to Kinesis Firehose", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2022-12-16T22:56:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2021/10/17/cgo-for-arm64-lambda-functions.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2021/10/17/cgo-for-arm64-lambda-functions.html", "title": "cgo for ARM64 Lambda Functions", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2021-10-17T23:05:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/10/15/cheap-serverless-containers-using-api-gateway.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/10/15/cheap-serverless-containers-using-api-gateway.html", "title": "Cheap serverless containers using API Gateway", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2022-10-15T23:47:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/10/16/cloudfront-and-lambda-function-urls.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2022/10/16/cloudfront-and-lambda-function-urls.html", "title": "CloudFront and Lambda function URLs", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2022-10-16T23:08:52+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2025/02/10/cloudfront-triggered-s3-data-event-formats.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2025/02/10/cloudfront-triggered-s3-data-event-formats.html", "title": "CloudFront-triggered S3 data event formats", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2025-02-10T05:32:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2026/06/19/cloudtrail-in-cloudwatch-isnt-very-good.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2026/06/19/cloudtrail-in-cloudwatch-isnt-very-good.html", "title": "CloudTrail in CloudWatch isn't very good", "content_html": "<p>Amazon has deprecated CloudTrail Lake as of 1st June 2026 for new customers. I\nassume this is due to lack of uptake. I never got around to properly using it,\nand I'm a CloudTrail fan! So I can only imagine not many others used it. In its\nplace, Amazon [recommends][ct-doc] that we \"explore CloudWatch\". I explored\nCloudWatch and came away quite disappointed.</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2026-06-19T04:08:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}, {"id": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2025/05/07/cloudtrail-wish-almost-granted.html", "url": "https://awsteele.com/blog/2025/05/07/cloudtrail-wish-almost-granted.html", "title": "CloudTrail wish: almost granted", "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-07-02T02:13:54+00:00", "date_published": "2025-05-07T00:50:00+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["AWS"]}]}